divs: Sighting DetailsAs I said was looking at all the stars at Night , after 10 minutes I thought I saw a shooting star high up in the atmosphere , but this star like light was heading in a straight line going north , I shouted my wife as I was shocked to see this , it was only a matter if minutes when I could no longer see the light moving with the naked eye , Amazing
